reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is a perfect fusion of Style and Functionality
reviews.reviewText: I purchased the Smart Watch upon the recommendation of my online personal trainer from ALTERED FITNESS, mainly to track my steps. However, this watch has exceeded my expectations! Not only does it efficiently track fitness activities, but it also comes with a variety of other useful features, all at a fantastic price point.Moreover, it flaunts a stylish design that blends with my work attire, making it versatile and suitable for every occasion. For anyone in need of a multifunctional, chic, and affordable smartwatch, this Smart Watch is a brilliant choice!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars It didn’t last
reviews.reviewText: I bought this on October 26. The app was not easy to use, and the watch often “stole” the Bluetooth connection. Then, six weeks in, the watch stopped holding a charge; though fully charged it stopped functioning in less than a day. Most disappointing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Works but buggy
reviews.reviewText: Had a hard time pairing with my phone. I wanted to use samsung health directly but it wouldn't let me. Simple layout on app, but features do not work seamlessly as the app states. I got notifications at first, but as soon as I used dnd they stopped working. I have it set for water and move reminders, got 0. It has not monitored my sleep yet at all, and I can find no instructions to set it up at all. Instructions are just upselling the product. No actual instructions at all. I can't get it to monitor anything automatically, I actually have to tap the screen to get it to do it. Seems relatively accurate, it came on time, and is cute and stylish, good price, but does not work as "advertised", and instructions? Don't bother.just packing material. If I can't get it to work, I'm returning.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Had to come back to edit this after a few days...The pink band and rose gold color is very pretty. Most of the apps are easily accessible. However, you cannot reply to messages. Unless someone has found a way please share with me. I've googled googled, can't find answers to help troubleshoot. The manual is a joke because its the size of the box it came it and probably less than 500 words. Not surprised considering it is an Amazon product. I figured it's worth is only if used for just tracking steps and heart rate. Just as any other Smartwatch don't even bother using the blood pressure feature, can't possibly be accurate. It's as stated by all the reports out there that in order to use the Smartwatch blood pressure feature, you should be calibrating with an actual arm cuff from time to time, otherwise as a standalone, it's just an estimate. If you know anything about how blood pressure is measured then you'd know it to be true that no watch can accurately measure your blood pressure without applying pressure. The reminder feature for drinking water only worked once then stopped working. I've reset, unpaired, and stilll doesn't fix that feature. The text message notifications ALSO stopped working after like the 1st day. So yeah...if you're just planning to use it for steps and HR then should be fine....for now.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It works and keeps track of fitness easily - works with Samsung
reviews.reviewText: I used this today for my fitness goals, and it tracked my heartrate and steps well. I climb steps and needed a watch that would do this, so I'm really happy about this one. It's easy to install the app, and you can change the face of the watch to a design you like, which is a plus for me. I'd say this is a user friendly gadget and I would recommend it. Easy to charge as well, and connects easily to my phone/bluetooth.
